New features v0.6 Samedi:
* Reviving Zombies.
* Massive improvements to vehicle physics and UI.
* Many new buildings and missions.

For latest discussions and news on Cataclysm DDA, please visit:
Homepage: http://www.cataclysmdda.com/
Forum: http://smf.cataclysmdda.com/
Wiki: http://wiki.cataclysmdda.com/

New configurable options:
Autosave frequency, Trigonometric (circular) distance,
Trait points cap, radiation lethality.

Ingame you can access the options via the help menu (?2).
